data.name: textBoxTabDescription.Text
data.value:
This tab allows you to export a data template and analysis scripts for analysis of an experiment conforming to the design specified. First specify the number of replicates that you want to use in the experiment.
The button Export analysis template will generate the following files: 1. A data template (.csv file format) to enter the actual observations from the experiment, and 2. A additional csv file specifying the contrasts of the comparison(s) (used by the analysis scripts). 3. A main analysis script file (in R) to run the analysis for a correctly filled data template csv file. 4. Additional R script files that are needed for running the analysis script.
